Emilio SUAREZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 3D18-1594 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 11, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed for lack of jurisdiction as untimely.
